Each set comes with 1Pcs multi-purpose stainless steel rack, 1Pcs skewer rack with 4 skewers, 100Pcs natural wood pulp paper liners, 1Pcs small size food tong & 1Pcs silicone brush.

PRACTICAL DESIGN, EASY TO USE - The multi-purpose air fryer rack allows for good air circulation and doubles up the products being cooked, no waste of space of the air fryer. And the skewer rack with 4 skewers which enables you to make kebabs and all sorts of other foodstuffs served on skewers. The greater has additional kitchen tongs, oil brush and 100Pcs paper liners as well as which make preparation, serving & cleaning a breeze.

HEALTHY MATERIALS, WELL MADE, EASY TO CLEAN - All items are made of quality 304 stainless steel material & food grade silicone while following strict quality control guidelines without relying on BPA or harsh materials. and a breeze to clean to make sure you can use them with peace of mind. QUALITY GUARANTEE & AFTER-SALE SERVICE - Please feel free to contact us if you have any issues before purchase or during use, we are here to help.
